16 TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING PERMISSIVE
17 SERVICE CREDIT FOR GAP YEAR SERVICE
18 UNDER THE ARKANSAS TEACHER RETIREMENT
19 SYSTEM; AND TO DECLARE AN EMERGENCY.
20
21 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
22
23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 24-7-202(23), concerning the definition of
24 “gap year” as applicable to the Arkansas Teacher Retirement System, is
25 amended to read as follows:
26 (23) “Gap year” "Gap period" means a period of time one-quarter
27 (1/4) of a fiscal year:
28 (A) In which a member:
29 (i) Was an inactive member; and
30 (ii) Either:
31 (a) Was unemployed; or
32 (b) Did not provide qualified service; and
33 (B) For which the system may grant the member permissive
34 service credit;
35
36 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code § 24-7-613 is amended to read as follows:
